<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- title  -->
    <title>TalenCrafter | Home </title>

    <!-- css file -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">

    <!-- google fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter&family=Lato&family=Montserrat&family=Poppins&family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- google icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />

    <!-- font awesome  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <!-- aos link  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />

    <!-- web icon -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/icons/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">

</head>
<body>
    <!-- nav bar -->
    <nav>
        <div class="title">
            <img src="images/logo1.png" alt="logo" class="logo">
        </div>
        <div class="login-options">
            <a href="/"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                home
            </span><p>Home</p></a>
            <a href="login" id="login-btn"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                person
            </span><p>Login/Register</p></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- main content  -->
    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <div class="lefthome">
                <h2>Elevate the search for your next career with <span>TalenCrafter</span></h2>
                <a href="/candidate/findjob"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                    search
                </span>Find job</a>
            </div>
            <div class="righthome">
                <img src="../images/job-finding.png" alt="job finding image" loading="lazy">
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="offer">
            <h3>What we <span>offer</span></h3>
            <div class="offers">
                <div class="resumebuilder" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="../images/resumebuilder.jpg" alt="resume builder images" loading="lazy"> 
                    <div class="description">
                        <p>Experience seamless resume creation with TalenCrafter's AI-powered Resume Builder.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#offer" class="readmore" id="resume">Read more<span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        arrow_right_alt
                    </span></a>
                </div>
                <div class="jobalert" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <img src="../images/discover.jpg" alt="job finding image" loading="lazy">
                    <div class="description">
                        <p>Explore career opportunities effortlessly with TalenCrafter's Discover Jobs feature. </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#offer" class="readmore" id="alert">Read more<span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        arrow_right_alt
                    </span></a>
                </div>
                <div class="discover" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <img src="../images/jobalert.jpg" alt="job alert image" loading="lazy">
                    <div class="description">
                        <p>Stay ahead in your job search with TalenCrafter's Job Alert feature. </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#offer" class="readmore" id="discovery">Read more<span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        arrow_right_alt
                    </span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <section id="popup">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="close">
                    close
                    </span>
                <h4 class="popupname">topic</h4>
                <p class="popupcontent">Stay ahead in your job search with TalenCrafter's Job Alert feature. Set personalized alerts for application deadlines, and receive timely notifications via email. Never miss an opportunity as our system keeps you informed when the application deadline is approaching. TalenCrafter is your proactive companion, ensuring you're always in the loop for potential career advancements.</p>
            </section>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <h3>About us</h3>
            <div class="aboutus">
                <div class="leftabout" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <p>In the fiercely competitive job market, securing the right opportunity is a formidable task, whether you're a student starting your career or an experienced professional seeking a change. TalenCrafter recognizes the intricacies of job finding and is committed to simplifying and empowering your journey. Our platform offers a seamless experience with tailored job matching and an intuitive AI-powered Resume Builder. Furthermore, our distinctive Job Alert feature ensures you stay informed as application deadlines approach, empowering you to submit applications promptly and stay ahead in the job search. Join TalenCrafter, where we prioritize simplicity and effectiveness, providing the tools you need for success in today's dynamic employment landscape. Your ideal job opportunity is just a click away!</p>
                    <a href="login.html" id="explore">Explore Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="rightabout" >
                    <img src="../images/jobsearch.jpg" alt="job finding image" loading="lazy">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="feedback">
                <div class="leftfeedback" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="../images/shareexp.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="rightfeedback" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <h3 id="exp">Share Your Experience with us</h3>
                    <form action="/mail/feedback" method="post">
                        <input type="text" name="fName" placeholder="First Name" autocomplete="off">
                        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter Email" autocomplete="off">
                        <textarea name="description" id="messagebox" placeholder="Message" autocomplete="off"></textarea>
                        <button>Send<span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                            send
                        </span></button>
                    </form>
                </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- footer   -->
    <footer>
        <div class="contactdetail">
            <div class="leftfooter">
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>aravind364kk30@gmail.com</p>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>+91 9342610087</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rightfooter">
                <p>Connect with social media</p>
                <div class="icons">
                    <a href=""><img src="../icons/instagram.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></a>
                    <a href=""><img src="../icons/facebook.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></a>
                    <a href=""><img src="../icons/linkedin.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></a>
                    <a href=""><img src="../icons/youtube.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p id="copyright">Copyright &copy; 2024 | All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <!-- aos animation -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({
            offset: 250,
            duration: 1000
        });
    </script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/home.js"></script>

</body>
</html>